task.summary: Implemented ability to load HTML files. The html files are read in and set as the body of the response.

Response bodies are always gzipped before being sent. This allows the server to send the same data in less bytes. Had to rework the entire PageLoader class to implement. Current PageLoader is a static class that has methods to return data-structures of the loaded body.

Implemented the existing simple API using a postgreSQL server implementation. The server loads the requested data from the users table with the JDBC plugin. The new APIHandler class handles the database connections and JSON parsing.
